                        <h3>Server Side Swift</h3>
                        <p>Create modern web apps, sites, and APIs using HTTP or real-time apps using WebSockets.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article>
                        <img src="/images/rocket.png" alt="Rocket">
                        <h3>Fast</h3>
                        <p>Nearly 100x faster than popular web frameworks using Ruby and PHP. Swift is fast by every meaning of the word.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article>
                        <img src="/images/lock.png" alt="Lock">
                        <h3>Secure</h3>
                        <p>Trusted encryption and TLS from OpenSSL and BCrypt hashing is included by default to make security easy.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article>
                        <img src="/images/graph.png" alt="Graph">
                        <h3>Extensible</h3>
                        <p>With middleware and Swift extensions, you can add custom functionality to Vapor that feels native.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article>
                        <img src="/images/terminal.png" alt="Terminal">
                        <h3>Expressive</h3>
                        <p>The static type system allows you to write less and do more. Vapor apps are very concise and even more powerful.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article>
                        <img src="/images/pacman.png" alt="Pacman">
                        <h3>Fun</h3>
                        <p>With autocomplete, debugging, and breakpoints you'll spend more time creating and less time fixing.</p>
